&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$222,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please see our Privacy Notice for details regarding Airtableâ€™s collection and use of personal information relating to the application and recruitment process by clicking&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.airtable.com/company/personnel-privacy-notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fKEf0G59m8RT2ZaOJyxoqQ3kW3oUaxhZ/view&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
