&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Analytical mindset with the ability to translate data into business insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li1&quot;&gt;Familiarity with technologies - Airtable, Greenhouse, Workramp, Glint, Gem etc&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
